---------------
GF-Calculator :
---------------


introduction :

    GF-Calculator is a program to preform addintion, subtraction and
    multiplication on two number in Galois Field 2^8.


Compile or Build & Run :

    To compile or Build and run GF-Calculator you have 2 ways 
	1- compile the source files
		a- cd src/
		b- gcc gf-calculator.c -o gf-calculator
		c- ./gf-calculator ---> to run the application. 
	2- Build GF-Calculator via make file 
		a- cd /Debug
		b- make gf-calculator
		c- ./gf-calculator ---> to run the application.

